of the earth’s atmosphere.]

00:05:38.731 --> 00:05:42.731
(Narrator) ♪ I whisper your name
from time to time. ♪

00:05:42.962 --> 00:05:44.942
[Keyboard clacking and guitar strumming]

00:05:45.162 --> 00:05:48.472
♪ I smell the drops the upon your hair

00:05:48.664 --> 00:05:52.064
and I take your hand in mine.

00:05:52.550 --> 00:05:54.920
And I hold you tight.

00:05:56.029 --> 00:05:58.259
I find your smile.

00:05:59.545 --> 00:06:04.445
And we both sigh. ♪

00:06:05.164 --> 00:06:09.164
